I am now seeing a therapist and am experiencing vision loss and extreme acid reflux. I also now suffer from vivid nightmares in which the diseased carrot pictured in the app crawls out from under my bed and attacks me. whatever you do, DO NOT DOWNLOAD THIS APP!!!
